{
  "texts": [
    "The Prompt Editor comprises three forms: basic prompt information (Fig. 2B), optional advanced settings (Fig.",
    "3), and optional sharing settings.",
    "In the basic prompt information section, users can configure the title, icon, and prompt template.",
    "The advanced settings allow more experienced users to set the LLM temperature, output parsing rules, and insertion rules (Fig. 3).",
    "To share a prompt with the community, users can provide a description, tags, and recommended LLM models in the sharing settings, and then click on the button."
  ]
}